2007-08-07  Lluis Sanchez Gual <lluis@novell.com> 

	* Mono.Addins.Database/AddinDatabase.cs,
	  Mono.Addins.Database/AddinHostIndex.cs,
	  Mono.Addins.Database/AddinScanFolderInfo.cs,
